@ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5267
@devToken = dev-token

### List HR events (dev auth — no Entra required)
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/hr-events
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}

### Submit HR event (Vodacom tenant)
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/hr-events
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idNumber": "8501015800084",
  "eventType": "GhostEmployee",
  "eventDate": "2026-03-15T00:00:00Z",
  "employerName": "Acme Holdings (Pty) Ltd",
  "employeeNumber": "EMP-4521",
  "verificationStatus": "Denied",
  "notes": "Local SQL dev test"
}

### Submit MNO event
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/mno-events
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idNumber": "8501015800084",
  "msisdn": "0821234567",
  "eventType": "NewSIMApplication",
  "eventDate": "2026-03-16T10:30:00Z",
  "applicationChannel": "InStore",
  "outletOrDealer": "CellShop Sandton City",
  "flagReason": "Velocity threshold exceeded"
}

### Anonymous fraud signals
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/fraud-signals
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}

### ID check
POST {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/lookup/id-check
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idNumber": "8501015800084"
}

### Dashboard stats
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}

### MTN tenant (switch tenant via header)
GET {{ComricFraudCalculatorBackend_HostAddress}}/api/v1/hr-events
Authorization: Bearer {{devToken}}
X-Dev-TenantId: 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
